Apples! They are a crunchy, portable snack that packs a nutritious punch and gives you that little pop of energy you need to get through the day. Whether diced in a salad, dipped in peanut butter, or eaten whole, the apple has become a staple food in any pantry.While you may love them for their tastiness, satisfying sweetness, and naturally convenient packaging, there are many other reasons to bite into apples. Click through the slideshow to learn more about this fantastic fruit.